WEBVTT

00:01:28.641 --> 00:01:32.066
to what they hope
will be freedom in the North.

00:01:33.665 --> 00:01:36.601
And there, with this young person

00:01:38.013 --> 00:01:41.998
as they are about to board that ship,

00:01:42.022 --> 00:01:43.442
that boat,

00:01:43.466 --> 00:01:46.728
that truck, that train,

00:01:46.752 --> 00:01:49.164
are the people who raised them.

00:01:49.946 --> 00:01:52.850
Their mother, their father,

00:01:52.874 --> 00:01:56.723
their aunt, their uncle,
their grandparents,

00:01:56.747 --> 00:02:00.524
whoever it might have been
who had gotten them to this point.